{"word":"G3615 - οἰκιακός - oikiakós - oy-kee-ak-os' - They of household","slug":"G3615","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">οἰκιακός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>oikiakós"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>oy-kee-ak-os'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>They of household"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"- Original: <b><el>οἰκιακός</el></b> <p />- Transliteration: <b>Oikiakos</b> <p />- Phonetic: <b>oy-kee-ak-os'</b> <p class=\"def\">- Definition: </p> <p class='li260'><b>1.</b> one belonging to the house </p> <p class='li260'><b>2.</b> one under control of the master of a house, whether a son or a servant </p> <p class=\"origin\"/>- Origin: from <a href=\"#/G3614\">G3614</a> <p />- TDNT entry: None <p />- Part(s) of speech: Noun Masculine <p />- Strong's: From <a href=\"#/G3614\">G3614</a>; <i>familiar</i> that is (as noun) <b><i>relatives</i></b>: - they (them) of (his own) household."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2026\">G2026</a>, <a href=\"#/G2731\">G2731</a>, <a href=\"#/G2732\">G2732</a>, <a href=\"#/G2733\">G2733</a>, <a href=\"#/G3609\">G3609</a>, <a href=\"#/G3611\">G3611</a>, <a href=\"#/G3613\">G3613</a>, <a href=\"#/G3614\">G3614</a>, <a href=\"#/G3616\">G3616</a>, <a href=\"#/G3617\">G3617</a>, <a href=\"#/G3618\">G3618</a>, <a href=\"#/G3619\">G3619</a>, <a href=\"#/G3620\">G3620</a>, <a href=\"#/G3621\">G3621</a>, <a href=\"#/G3622\">G3622</a>, <a href=\"#/G3623\">G3623</a>, <a href=\"#/G3624\">G3624</a>, <a href=\"#/G4925\">G4925</a>"}]}